data.description: Welcome to your new home sweet home! Picture this: a charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath brick home that embraces you with its original hardwood floors. Step into the kitchen and living room, adorned with wood-look tile and extra-large space for all your gatherings. The two spacious living areas ensure you have room to spread out and entertain guests effortlessly. Imagine relaxing in the sizable backyard, perfect for unwinding or hosting memorable get-togethers. And the best part? The seller is generously offering $3,000.00 towards your closing costs with an acceptable offer! Please keep in mind that this wonderful home is being SOLD AS-IS. Agents, don't forget to check out the additional remarks for more details.
